rows.label: CoCaption1_01
rows.name:
The enterprise that forms the heart of
the Sakuraba Group. Respected for
the quality of their workmanship.

rows.label: CoCaption1_02
rows.name:
An up-and-coming Spanish arms
company devoted almost entirely to
beam-technology research.

rows.label: CoCaption1_03
rows.name:
A startup seeking to open a new era
of weapons development based on
tech obtained from the Growth.

rows.label: CoCaption1_04
rows.name:
An end-to-end enterprise started for
fun by the Ma-non. Its purpose is to
develop products that help protect life.

rows.label: CoCaption1_05
rows.name:
The local branch of a Larsian arms-dev
group. It's named after the six military
strategists who formed the company.

rows.label: CoCaption1_06
rows.name:
A group formed by Orpheans who
fled the Growth. Their gear is much
different than that of human make.

rows.label: CoCaption1_07
rows.name:
This enterprise is part of the Nopon
Commerce Guild, which originally
began by trading fruits and nuts.

rows.label: CoCaption1_08
rows.name:
An individual dealer with unique taste.
He has a large following of quiet,
but extremely loyal, customers.

rows.label: CoCaption2_01
rows.name:
Their weapons are known for stability,
but they lag behind in resistance against
attributes other than physical.

rows.label: CoCaption2_02
rows.name:
Their main products are focused on
beam attributesâ€”their beam-resistant
ground gear is a best seller.

rows.label: CoCaption2_03
rows.name:
Their equipment uses ether technology,
which is difficult to work with. Perhaps
that's why stability is lacking.

rows.label: CoCaption2_04
rows.name:
They excel in high-defense ground gear,
and are expanding their market further
with bolt-attribute weapons.

rows.label: CoCaption2_05
rows.name:
Their weapons boast high damage,
and work under the theory that user
skill can make up for their inaccuracy.

rows.label: CoCaption2_06
rows.name:
They mainly build products with high
evasion, but their best seller is a line
of gravity-attribute weapons.

rows.label: CoCaption2_07
rows.name:
Nearly all of their weapons have
thermal attributes. Many models are
modified for greater magazine capacity.

rows.label: CoCaption2_08
rows.name:
He provides rare and valuable gravity-
attribute products. Known for attention
to detail in both form and function.
